snippet.title: STARWHAL Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Flopping onto PC and Mac in its fully evolved form - STARWHAL is the 4 player party phenomenon that will change your life.

Find out more and try out the demo!
http://www.starwhal.com

Check the game out on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/263020/
